{"thi-ap15:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap15:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap15:0.3":"Pancadipadayikatheriapadana ","thi-ap15:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","thi-ap15:1.2":"cariki asaham tada; ","thi-ap15:1.3":"Aramena ca aramam, ","thi-ap15:1.4":"carami kusalatthika. ","thi-ap15:2.1":"Kalapakkhamhi divase, ","thi-ap15:2.2":"addasam bodhimuttamam; ","thi-ap15:2.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","thi-ap15:2.4":"bodhimule nisidaham. ","thi-ap15:3.1":"Garucittam upatthetva, ","thi-ap15:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","thi-ap15:3.3":"Somanassam pavedetva, ","thi-ap15:3.4":"evam cintesi tavade. ","thi-ap15:4.1":"‘Yadi buddho amitaguno, ","thi-ap15:4.2":"asamappatipuggalo; ","thi-ap15:4.3":"Dassetu patihiram me, ","thi-ap15:4.4":"bodhi obhasatu ayam’. ","thi-ap15:5.1":"Saha avajjite mayham, ","thi-ap15:5.2":"bodhi pajjali tavade; ","thi-ap15:5.3":"Sabbasonnamaya asi, ","thi-ap15:5.4":"disa sabba virocati. ","thi-ap15:6.1":"Sattarattindivam tattha, ","thi-ap15:6.2":"bodhimule nisidaham; ","thi-ap15:6.3":"Sattame divase patte, ","thi-ap15:6.4":"dipapujam akasaham. ","thi-ap15:7.1":"Asanam parivaretva, ","thi-ap15:7.2":"panca dipani pajjalum; ","thi-ap15:7.3":"Yava udeti suriyo, ","thi-ap15:7.4":"dipa me pajjalum tada. ","thi-ap15:8.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap15:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap15:8.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap15:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap15:9.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","thi-ap15:9.2":"pancadipati vuccati; ","thi-ap15:9.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","thi-ap15:9.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","thi-ap15:10.1":"Asankhiyani dipani, ","thi-ap15:10.2":"parivare jalimsu me; ","thi-ap15:10.3":"Yavata devabhavanam, ","thi-ap15:10.4":"dipalokena jotati. ","thi-ap15:11.1":"Parammukha nisiditva, ","thi-ap15:11.2":"yadi icchami passitum; ","thi-ap15:11.3":"Uddham adho ca tiriyam, ","thi-ap15:11.4":"sabbam passami cakkhuna. ","thi-ap15:12.1":"Yavata abhikankhami, ","thi-ap15:12.2":"datthum sugataduggate; ","thi-ap15:12.3":"Tattha avaranam natthi, ","thi-ap15:12.4":"rukkhesu pabbatesu va. ","thi-ap15:13.1":"Asiti devarajunam, ","thi-ap15:13.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap15:13.3":"Satanam cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap15:13.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap15:14.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","thi-ap15:14.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","thi-ap15:14.3":"Dipasatasahassani, ","thi-ap15:14.4":"parivare jalanti me. ","thi-ap15:15.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","thi-ap15:15.2":"uppajjim matukucchiyam; ","thi-ap15:15.3":"Matukucchigata santi, ","thi-ap15:15.4":"akkhi me na nimilati. ","thi-ap15:16.1":"Dipasatasahassani, ","thi-ap15:16.2":"punnakammasamangita; ","thi-ap15:16.3":"Jalanti sutikagehe, ","thi-ap15:16.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap15:17.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap15:17.2":"manasam vinivattayim; ","thi-ap15:17.3":"Ajaramatam sitibhavam, ","thi-ap15:17.4":"nibbanam phassayim aham. ","thi-ap15:18.1":"Jatiya sattavassaham, ","thi-ap15:18.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","thi-ap15:18.3":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","thi-ap15:18.4":"gunamannaya gotamo. ","thi-ap15:19.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","thi-ap15:19.2":"sunnagare vasantiya; ","thi-ap15:19.3":"Sada pajjalate dipam, ","thi-ap15:19.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap15:20.1":"Dibbacakkhuvisuddham me, ","thi-ap15:20.2":"samadhikusala aham; ","thi-ap15:20.3":"Abhinnaparamippatta, ","thi-ap15:20.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap15:21.1":"Sabbavositavosana, ","thi-ap15:21.2":"katakicca anasava; ","thi-ap15:21.3":"Pancadipa mahavira, ","thi-ap15:21.4":"pade vandami cakkhuma. ","thi-ap15:22.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap15:22.2":"yam dipamadadim tada; ","thi-ap15:22.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap15:22.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap15:23.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap15:23.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap15:23.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap15:24.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap15:24.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap15:24.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap15:25.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap15:25.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap15:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap15:26.1":"Ittham sudam pancadipadayika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap15:27.1":"Pancadipadayikatheriyapadanam pancamam. "}